embed.alt: A 3D Pixar-style grumpy cartoon cat, ultra-expressive face, detailed fur, big round eyes narrowed in irritation, standing in a warm, colorful kitchen. On the counter sits a perfectly frosted celebration cake. The cat clenches an oversized cartoonish 3D fist, squash-and-stretch physics, and with exaggerated Pixar-style anticipation, comically smashes the cake in one dramatic slow-in/fast-out motion. Frosting bursts into the air in soft, realistic particles; sprinkles fly in all directions; the cake collapses in a satisfying 3D splat. Playful orchestral music, dynamic camera move, soft global illumination, and subtle depth of field. End with the cat, now covered in frosting, giving a classic Pixar-style annoyed glare straight into the camera.
